body:
## What happened

- Sort members in Dart file (e.g., main.dart)
- Change files referenced from it (e.g., imported class names)
- Reformat with dartfmt (not sure about this one, maybe it doesn't affect it or maybe it comes after the next one)
- Try to undo several times

## Version information

Android Studio `3.4` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 35.3.1` • Dart plugin `183.6270`

Error getting Flutter sdk information.
